{"data":[{"id":560370252,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560370252","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545832552,"updated_time":1545832552,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":37,"comment_count":9,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e我回答的时候看到的题目是“如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？”，没有看到更详细的描述。下面充斥清一色的冷嘲热讽，好不欢乐。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我要支持一下高中生的勇气，以防止他因为心灰意冷而丧失了对数学生涯的追求。现实中做数学研究你得适应失败。谁还没有个痴心妄想的时候呢，治疗虚妄的良药是阅读，交流，向领域内大师学习。即便在别人看来你提的问题很傻，是错误荒谬的，不要停止提问。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e之所以能提出这样的问题，我觉得很大程度上是因为国内数学科普做得还不够好，以至于连一个热爱数学的高中生都没有意识到哥德巴赫猜想这个问题的难度。在数学中，这种问题属于容易读懂，但证明起来特别复杂。类似于哥德巴赫猜想的问题还有费马大定理[1]等。最好的结果——被清华北大数学系保送，此结果为你从事数学研究继而成为数学家铺平了道路，那数学家群体是怎么看待这个问题的呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003eThis problem has the great virtue of being easy to\u003cbr\u003eunderstand, which makes it appealing in the way that\u003cbr\u003efermat’s last theorem [V.12] and goldbach’s conjecture\u003cbr\u003e[V.30] are appealing. And yet, it is not a central\u003cbr\u003eproblem in the way that those two are: most mathematicians\u003cbr\u003ewould put it into a mental box marked\u003cbr\u003e“recreational” and forget about it.[2]\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e[1]这个问题从提出到解决花了\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fermat%2527s_Last_Theorem\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e358\u003c/a\u003e年的时间，有中译本的\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E8%25B4%25B9%25E9%25A9%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2590%2586%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%25AA%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%2583%2591%25E4%25BA%2586%25E4%25B8%2596%25E9%2597%25B4%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%2580%2585358%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25B0%259C/5549385\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e科普读物\u003c/a\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e[2]\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Princeton_Companion_to_Mathematics\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eThe Princeton Companion to Mathematics\u003c/a\u003e 第71页。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e[3]陶哲轩关于大问题的\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/dont-prematurely-obsess-on-a-single-big-problem-or-big-theory/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e人生经验\u003c/a\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"我回答的时候看到的题目是“如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？”，没有看到更详细的描述。下面充斥清一色的冷嘲热讽，好不欢乐。我要支持一下高中生的勇气，以防止他因为心灰意冷而丧失了对数学生涯的追求。现实中做数学研究你得适…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"taglin